http://www.coda.com/pim/schemas/matching

Root Elements

PIMMatchingRequest

The Root element for the PIMMatching service request

PIMMatchingResponse

The Root element for the PIMMatching service response

PIMMatchingSelectorRequest

This service allows you to select documents for matching.

PIMMatchingSelectorResponse

This is the response that is returned when you select documents for matching.

Function to kick off the background matching process from within the interactive matching client. The user could have modified the matching master at runtime.

CreateGroupRequest

The CreateGroupRequest type has Request as its base type.

CreateGroup.

Creates a group from some invoice and lrn lines.

Child elements

Name Minimum Maximum Type Description
MatchingMaster 1 1 MatchingMaster

The matching master to use.

GroupList 1 1 GroupList

List of groups that this new one will reference. This will be by way of LRN lines that have been split. It is likely that the group may not be related to any other in which case none need to be passed in.

InvoiceKeyKeyList 1 1 InvoiceKeyList

The keys for the invoices to put in the group.

LrnLineKeyKeyList 1 1 LRNLineKeyList

The keys for the lrn lines to put in the group. The keys are passed if the line hasn't been loaded up by the client before.

LrnLineList 1 1 LRNLineList

The lrn lines to put in the group. The full line should be passed in if it has been loaded up by the client before.
